Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.84,0:00:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}douban@LoudCrazyHeart\N参考豆瓣@爱看电影的猫 指出的翻译错误进行了部分修改
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.84,0:00:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,《一座军营》\NA Barracks
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.84,0:00:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这是337团炮兵部队驻地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.28,0:00:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}179师 临汾旅\N原属南京军区60军的179师('临汾旅')调归南京军区第12集团军建制\N
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.28,0:00:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,60军179师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.00,0:01:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在这样的房间里住了几个星期了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.60,0:01:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就可以观察连队日常活动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.16,0:02:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,现在是早上5点半
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.24,0:02:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我是个炮兵团参谋长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.96,0:02:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫吴汉海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.40,0:02:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我是1953年志愿参军的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.32,0:02:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我家住在安徽省
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.12,0:02:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,庐江县
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.36,0:02:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我是贫农出生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.72,0:02:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我家里有5口人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.00,0:02:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,三个孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.32,0:02:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,还有我爱人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.20,0:02:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,爱人叫朱沈兰 在肥皂厂工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.52,0:02:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这里我和副参谋长住在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.32,0:02:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,他在那边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.48,0:02:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫王根生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.84,0:03:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,1937年生的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.40,0:03:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是安徽的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.88,0:03:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,和参谋长来自同一个地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.36,0:03:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我是1956年志愿参军的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.56,0:03:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我家里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.96,0:03:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我结婚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.32,0:03:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,还有一个小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.48,0:03:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱人在工厂工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.48,0:03:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,她通过工作为共产主义做贡献
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.44,0:03:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我们的办公室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.20,0:03:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这是他的桌子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.32,0:03:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.32,0:03:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我们两个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.92,0:03:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,共用这个柜子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.24,0:03:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,上面是他的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.04,0:03:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,下面是我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.96,0:03:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我们放些书籍和杂物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.56,0:03:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,这里可以看到营房
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.60,0:03:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那里还有一个篮球场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.64,0:04:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我经常和大家打球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.24,0:04:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我很喜欢打球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.88,0:04:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我们成了军官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.16,0:04:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,从群众中选出来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.32,0:04:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,士兵选的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.72,0:04:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在党支部讨论候选人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.68,0:04:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,上级党委批的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.32,0:04:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,这样就成了军官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.64,0:04:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,有没有军官学校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.68,0:04:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,军官学校有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.68,0:04:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.96,0:04:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,它们不是很重要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.92,0:04:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,主要是帮助干部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.96,0:04:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,帮助干部提高业务水平和技能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.32,0:04:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,干部主要还是在实地训练
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.60,0:04:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,工作日都是怎么安排的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.36,0:05:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,一个星期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.96,0:05:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有四天军事训练
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.92,0:05:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,一天政治学习
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.28,0:05:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,半天党委活动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.88,0:05:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,半天共青团的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.68,0:05:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,星期六下午是共青团活动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.32,0:05:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,时间很紧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.32,0:05:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,主要是连队活动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.56,0:05:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,比如
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.88,0:05:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,生产，补课
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.72,0:05:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,大概10点的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.32,0:05:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,士兵们可以休息一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.12,0:07:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,每个星期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.32,0:07:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,每个班班长和军官们会开一次会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.40,0:07:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,如果可以开始的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.72,0:08:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就开始吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.80,0:08:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,下面我来讲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.08,0:08:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我把我们班给连队军官的意见收集了一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.52,0:08:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.32,0:08:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我给各位班长和军官解释一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.32,0:08:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,一共有三条
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.76,0:08:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,第一条
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.76,0:08:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,是说班长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.72,0:08:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,对规章制度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.36,0:08:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不够严格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.32,0:08:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,具体来说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.20,0:08:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,每天定时清洁武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.80,0:08:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,有时候没有监督
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.80,0:08:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,第二点呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.92,0:08:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,对厨房管理不够严格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.20,0:08:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我们注意到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.08,0:08:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我们浪费了一些食物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.40,0:09:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,每天浪费一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.32,0:09:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,全年就浪费很多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.32,0:09:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,如果全军都这么浪费食物的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.96,0:09:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,后果就太严重了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.64,0:09:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,连长们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.80,0:09:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这方面要更加严格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.80,0:09:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的连长同志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.80,0:09:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,非常负责任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.96,0:09:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,他要求比较高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.32,0:09:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,训练的时候非常严格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.48,0:09:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.32,0:09:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,有时候他的批评并不都是对的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.84,0:09:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,有时候批评过多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.28,0:09:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,比如
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.48,0:09:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,有些新同志身体没达标
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.24,0:09:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,必须加强锻炼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.32,0:09:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,连长不应该只是批评他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.32,0:09:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,而是应该帮助他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.40,0:09:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,指出他们的弱点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.32,0:10:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是我们对连长的意见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.40,0:10:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得有些事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.96,0:10:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,连队的军官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.16,0:10:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,比如说我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.64,0:10:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,在政治工作方面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.32,0:10:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,做得不够好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.52,0:10:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不，不，这不是你的错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.32,0:10:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,主要是我的错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.92,0:10:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不，是我的错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.40,0:10:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,所有的班长都已经发言了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.32,0:10:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我们班一个同志把一片面包掉到了地上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.56,0:10:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,他就给猪吃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.08,0:10:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,指导员看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.20,0:10:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,他没有去找他单独谈心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.32,0:10:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,而是在大会上当着全连队的面 公开批评了他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.32,0:10:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得他的批评是对的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.16,0:10:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,但是他的方式错了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.32,0:10:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,每次批评都要找到最佳的方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.48,0:10:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,首长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.84,0:10:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你说指导员没有处理好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.32,0:10:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得所有的错误都要批评
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.28,0:10:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不管怎样都要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.84,0:11:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得我们要强调批评的方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.24,0:11:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我不同意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.56,0:11:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,每个错误都要批评
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.32,0:11:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,军队必须要有严格标准
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.44,0:11:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.76,0:11:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我们批评的方法也要有严格标准
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.48,0:11:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得我们的批评要小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.32,0:11:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,方法要正确
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.32,0:11:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要知道批评会造成什么后果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.68,0:11:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,批评的目的是教育
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.56,0:11:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们想教育
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.56,0:11:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,就要用正确的方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.68,0:11:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我受益匪浅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.32,0:11:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,有其他的评语吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.04,0:11:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那大会结束了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.84,0:11:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,那就散会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.40,0:11:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,在中国，参军是很光荣的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.52,0:11:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,尽管年满18岁都可以当兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.32,0:11:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不是每个想当兵的人都能当
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.40,0:12:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,也许最重要的是力量和性格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.92,0:12:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,比如要忠诚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.96,0:12:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,阶级背景也很重要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.12,0:12:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,工人和农民的儿子最好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.12,0:12:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,尽管大部分年轻人都想参军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.92,0:12:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,15个人里面只会入选1人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.00,0:12:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,今天的菜单是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.32,0:12:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,辣椒炒肉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.32,0:12:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,茄子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.48,0:12:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,汤和米饭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.84,0:13:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,他是连长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.60,0:13:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我是指导员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.12,0:13:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,他是副连长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.88,0:13:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,他是通讯员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.08,0:13:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,文书
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.32,0:13:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,炊事员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.76,0:13:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,他也是通讯员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.80,0:13:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,军官都是和战士们一起吃饭吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.52,0:13:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.20,0:13:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这是干部和战士团结的一方面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.32,0:13:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这样的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.72,0:13:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我们面对的是共同的困难
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.00,0:13:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,干部和战士在政治上是平等的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.04,0:13:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,同劳动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.32,0:14:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,同吃饭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.16,0:14:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,同娱乐同训练
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.60,0:14:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,干部和战士吃的一样吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.32,0:14:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，我们干部和战士吃的是一样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.32,0:14:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,看那边的桌子 伙食是一样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.40,0:14:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么没有穿军衔肩章之类的东西呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.32,0:14:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,带军衔疏远了干部和战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.08,0:14:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,没有军衔官兵就在一起了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.44,0:14:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,什么时候取消了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.32,0:14:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,1965年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.08,0:14:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那怎么样区别军官和战士？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.88,0:15:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,军官的衣服有四个口袋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.24,0:15:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,战士的只有两个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.84,0:15:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么会多些口袋？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.12,0:15:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,战士前面要带东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.32,0:15:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,口袋多了就很麻烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.32,0:15:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,但是军官可以放文件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.64,0:15:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我们努力做到自给自足
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.72,0:15:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你看到这些蔬菜了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.20,0:15:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,都是自己种的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.08,0:15:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,肉也是自己养的家禽的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.96,0:15:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,今天早上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.76,0:15:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我参加了连长和班长的会议
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.08,0:15:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我解释了你们所有的意见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.60,0:15:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,关于连长和连队干部的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.76,0:15:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,他们都同意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.08,0:16:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,做了自我批评
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.32,0:16:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,会议期间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.52,0:16:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,对某些事情也有不同意见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.76,0:16:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,比如
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.32,0:16:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那块浪费的面包
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.32,0:16:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,有的人认为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.84,0:16:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,辅导员当着全连队批评的方法是错误的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.32,0:16:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,有的人觉得他的方法是对的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.60,0:16:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我们讨论了这个问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.96,0:16:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,根据原则解决了这个问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.12,0:16:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,人都是一分为二的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.60,0:16:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,个人和行为是不同的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.96,0:16:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,这就意味着批评必须是针对他的错误的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.80,0:16:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,而不是这个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.12,0:16:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,大家还有什么其他想说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.36,0:16:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,或者有什么问题要问
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.32,0:16:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,都可以提出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.60,0:16:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的讨论会提高连队工作效率
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.32,0:17:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,也有利于祖国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.28,0:17:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不，就是这些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.32,0:17:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的意见连长都记下来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.36,0:17:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,特别是八班对我的批评
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.84,0:17:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,理由很充分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.04,0:17:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,关于批评面包的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.48,0:17:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我的调查研究不够充分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.16,0:17:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不够
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.36,0:17:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.36,0:17:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我有点武断
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.76,0:17:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,也许太武断了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.32,0:17:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,太武断了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.84,0:17:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我很高兴你们提出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.32,0:17:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我感觉这样很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.48,0:18:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你们必须站直身体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.48,0:18:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,抓紧绳子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.56,0:18:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,才能和身体协调好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.48,0:18:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,找到正确的角度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.32,0:18:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,左脚这样后退一步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.32,0:18:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,伸出右手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.32,0:18:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,拿着绳子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.16,0:18:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,左脚向后跨一步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.32,0:18:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,脸转向班长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.24,0:18:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,明不明白？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.04,0:18:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.88,0:18:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,那就试一次吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.12,0:18:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.32,0:19:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,对了，不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.32,0:19:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,还再偏一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.88,0:19:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,到这边来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.28,0:19:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,然后就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.32,0:19:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这就很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.68,0:19:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,等着信号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.96,0:19:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.08,0:19:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,班长下口令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.32,0:19:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,预备，开炮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.84,0:19:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.68,0:19:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你进步了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.52,0:19:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,做得更好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.44,0:19:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你看，我做一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.28,0:19:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,接着做什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.20,0:19:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,向右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.76,0:19:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,右脚向前一步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.28,0:19:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,右脚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.08,0:19:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,然后是左脚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.88,0:19:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,先把头放进去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.64,0:19:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,然后低头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.12,0:20:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你站起来的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.28,0:20:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,用力向前推
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.32,0:20:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,用最大的力推
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.76,0:20:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,这是临汾战役的模型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.92,0:20:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,1948年红军对战国民党军队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.68,0:20:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,通过重视这场战役 军官们学习人民军是怎样打仗的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.48,0:20:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,毛泽东制定的原则
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.08,0:20:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,在30年的战事中得到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.12,0:20:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,至今仍然有意义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.48,0:21:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,1927年红军势力很小
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.16,0:21:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,只有两千人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.32,0:21:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,只能躲在山里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.44,0:21:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,现在已经是人民解放军了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.84,0:21:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,有80万大军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.28,0:21:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,问题是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.16,0:21:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,现在国家的军队能否抵挡住各种敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.52,0:21:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,他们已经经历了长期痛苦的政治斗争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.08,0:21:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,和苏联紧密的联系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.88,0:21:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,文化大革命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.32,0:21:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,和林彪的斗争等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.28,0:21:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,现在主要是如何保持革命时期的精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.32,0:21:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我参加了这场战役
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.96,0:22:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我会尽量回答大家的问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.44,0:22:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,如果漏了什么的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.68,0:22:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,参谋长肯定会帮我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.88,0:22:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你不会的，讲吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.12,0:22:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,攻关以后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.12,0:22:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,敌军以为会在这边重新开战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.40,0:22:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,所以他们派了队伍到东门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.56,0:22:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我们驻扎在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.32,0:22:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,攻击敌军的弱点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.64,0:22:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,当时制造了一场爆炸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.52,0:22:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,爆炸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.08,0:22:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,在爆炸的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.00,0:22:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我们发动了攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.20,0:22:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我们军队一部分人去了右边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.96,0:22:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,有些去了左边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.16,0:22:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,其他的在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.04,0:22:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.32,0:22:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,还有这附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.16,0:23:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,包围然后冲破敌军的防守线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.68,0:23:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,在参战之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.96,0:23:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,战士们就已经讨论过战术了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.64,0:23:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,一会儿他们会讨论当时的情况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.96,0:23:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,他们想把军队民主落实到实践
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.96,0:23:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,参谋长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.60,0:23:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的战术取决于
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.92,0:23:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,敌军的位置、地形、我们的目标
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.52,0:23:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,敌人的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.56,0:23:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,就在敌军的强力部队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:39.24,0:23:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的主要目标
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.32,0:23:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,是打开通道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:42.24,0:23:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,在五班的帮助下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.32,0:23:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,到两三点的时候把敌军清理干净
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.16,0:23:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,那么我们该采用怎样的战术？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.12,0:23:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,谁想回答？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.28,0:23:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,毛主席教育我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.32,0:24:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,一次只攻击敌人的一个弱点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.08,0:24:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,确保彻底消灭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.56,0:24:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,然后一举攻破所有敌军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.92,0:24:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,最好在这里进攻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.32,0:24:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,就在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.96,0:24:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,地形很险恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.32,0:24:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以抵挡敌军的火炮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:19.48,0:24:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得我们最好从这里突破
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:22.68,0:24:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,还有在这前面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.88,0:24:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,因为和我们的据点近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:26.52,0:24:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我不同意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:28.48,0:24:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,解释下为什么不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:30.00,0:24:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得我们不应该从右进攻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:33.48,0:24:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,因为地势险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:36.20,0:24:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不易分散
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:38.00,0:24:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我们从这里的话会暴露
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:41.00,0:24:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,因为人太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:42.32,0:24:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,但是不暴露我们也可以消灭敌军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:45.80,0:24:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,从左边好很多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:47.32,0:24:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,因为这里有个深谷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:49.32,0:24:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,可以保护我们不受敌军炮火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:51.32,0:24:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,但是这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:52.68,0:24:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,更容易包围、攻陷 然后消灭敌军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:59.00,0:24:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,好吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:00.04,0:25:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:03.44,0:25:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我的计划
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:05.20,0:25:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,第二组
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:07.72,0:25:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,在右边据点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:10.00,0:25:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,大概离这里50码
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:14.04,0:25:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,第一组
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:15.32,0:25:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,就在他们前面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:17.32,0:25:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,第三组在树林旁边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:19.32,0:25:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:20.84,0:25:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,各就各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:16.56,0:27:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,闭上嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:18.48,0:27:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,请注意自己的舌头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:22.20,0:27:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,深呼吸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:24.68,0:27:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,然后用嘴用力吹乐器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:27.24,0:27:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我来演示一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:38.00,0:29:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,现在开始训练
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:40.20,0:29:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,预备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:00.24,0:30:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,都明白了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:04.64,0:30:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我来演示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:06.36,0:30:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你指出错误
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:13.32,0:30:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你防守，我来攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:26.32,0:30:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你们看到了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:27.36,0:30:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,每次我都没打到他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:31.32,0:30:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,同志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:32.24,0:30:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你的攻击基本行得通
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:34.04,0:30:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我看出了两个弱点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:35.56,0:30:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,首先
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:36.32,0:30:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,动作不够快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:38.96,0:30:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:39.88,0:30:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,然后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:41.28,0:30:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你的目标不够好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:43.44,0:30:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你的攻击应该更加用力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:47.84,0:30:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我做给你们看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:48.72,0:30:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:56.32,0:30:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:57.44,0:30:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我的动作太松散了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:59.56,0:31:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,还有一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:01.60,0:31:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,出步枪之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:03.72,0:31:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你后退了一步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:05.12,0:31:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,对手就可以抓住这一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:08.08,0:31:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你后退的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:10.16,0:31:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,就失去了主动性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:12.20,0:31:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,还有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:14.00,0:31:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你出步枪的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:15.32,0:31:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,没有向前一步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:18.20,0:31:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你举得太高了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:19.84,0:31:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,敌人会发现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:22.32,0:31:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你的攻击才失败了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:24.52,0:31:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,这些批评都很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:33.04,0:31:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,向左转
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:33.96,0:31:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,左转
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:34.76,0:31:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,向前转
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:35.60,0:31:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,预备跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:54.32,0:31:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这个师的战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:55.84,0:31:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,一共种植了838亩地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:59.12,0:32:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,每个营都种植农场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:01.32,0:32:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,每个连队都要在自己的地盘种蔬菜、养猪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:52.28,0:32:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我在连队负责经费支出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:56.20,0:33:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我是五班的战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:01.76,0:33:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,老家是山东的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:04.32,0:33:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,71年当兵的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:07.04,0:33:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我是当地选出来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:10.32,0:33:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,进了金融委员会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:14.32,0:33:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我和司令员、首长一起工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:18.28,0:33:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我们和每个连、每个班进行讨论
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:23.48,0:33:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,会议之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:26.28,0:33:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我们决定成立委员会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:29.24,0:33:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,党委批准了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:33.88,0:33:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,金融委员会的主要工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:38.32,0:33:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,是监控主要的财政支出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:42.12,0:33:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,金融委员会还负责管理生产
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:46.32,0:33:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，我们还管生产
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:49.00,0:33:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,还有所有的小笔支出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:51.48,0:33:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,比如俱乐部等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:54.20,0:33:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:56.32,0:33:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,检查看看有没有什么问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:09.64,0:34:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,给，你检查一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:12.32,0:34:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:17.08,0:34:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你看完之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:19.00,0:34:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,蒋康福会抄一遍张贴出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:45.96,0:34:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,金融委员会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:48.60,0:34:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,是部队实行经济民主的一种方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:52.32,0:34:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,政治、军队和经济民主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:55.96,0:34:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,在中国被称为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:58.36,0:35:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,三大民主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:06.32,0:35:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,部队已经实现了百分之八十自给自足
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:09.00,0:35:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,包括伙食
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:10.40,0:35:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,日常用品和一些武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:13.32,0:35:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,部队不想拖全国经济的后腿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:17.08,0:35:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,也不想在社会中担任领导角色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:21.32,0:35:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,中心思想是军人和普通工人是一样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:26.88,0:35:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,干部每天轮流在厨房劳动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:30.32,0:35:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,每年一个月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:32.44,0:35:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,军官又成了普通战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:54.44,0:35:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,少一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:03.40,0:36:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,小心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:15.92,0:36:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,把火停了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:59.52,0:37:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,这些豆子磨成了豆浆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:10.72,0:37:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,然后被用于
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:12.32,0:37:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,各种不同的食物中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:14.24,0:37:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,是伙食中常有的菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:42.32,0:37:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,剩下的猪油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:44.96,0:37:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,连队会自己制作肥皂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:54.76,0:37:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,也有一少部分女战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:56.96,0:37:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,主要是在空军和海军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:59.28,0:38:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,但是整体来说部队里女人很少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:03.00,0:38:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这些妇女不是部队的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:05.44,0:38:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,他们是军官的妻子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:14.72,0:38:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,为了自给自足
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:17.00,0:38:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,他们在一起做肥皂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:20.52,0:38:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,他们自己做了这个机器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:41.32,0:38:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,孙文洋是连长的妻子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:44.76,0:38:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,她家距离营地差不多250米
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:48.00,0:38:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,她的丈夫和其他军官住在营地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:51.88,0:38:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,他每周只回家一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:31.60,0:39:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,安静点，冷静
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:34.32,0:39:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈做饭的时候别说话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:40.48,0:39:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你在写家庭作业吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:42.32,0:39:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸，你回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:45.32,0:39:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，我在写作业
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:47.32,0:39:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:49.32,0:39:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,呆在这儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:50.52,0:39:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:52.92,0:39:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我数学分数很高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:03.00,0:40:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,别这么自私
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:05.72,0:40:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,给他看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:06.52,0:40:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,给你哥哥看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:17.28,0:40:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈在做饭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:18.72,0:40:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,很快就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:24.68,0:40:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我饿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:26.84,0:40:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:28.36,0:40:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我想吃糖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:30.36,0:40:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:32.84,0:40:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我想吃糖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:34.36,0:40:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,等一会儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:41.48,0:40:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,很快就给你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:43.00,0:40:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,但是不准哭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:48.08,0:40:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:48.56,0:40:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你的口琴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:59.32,0:41:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,共产主义改革之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:00.92,0:41:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,红军就有了轻工业的传统
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:04.76,0:41:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这项传统在文革期间得到了发展
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:08.52,0:41:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这个车间生产的医药产品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:11.60,0:41:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,20世纪70年代就开始作业了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:14.44,0:41:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,以前军官的妻子都是家庭主妇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:17.32,0:41:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,但是现在她们都在这样的车间工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:39.08,0:41:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你们在做什么药啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:43.32,0:41:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,红眼素（？？？）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:45.56,0:41:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,谁会用呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:48.96,0:41:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,主要是部队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:51.32,0:41:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,还有多余的话就会零售
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:57.00,0:41:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你丈夫是做什么的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:00.40,0:42:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,他是团里的政治部主任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:04.80,0:42:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你的丈夫是级别很高的军官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:10.48,0:42:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,团里主任嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:15.72,0:42:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫徐山花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:20.92,0:42:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱人叫王栓福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:22.96,0:42:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,他是一级军官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:30.60,0:42:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱人是团里面的副参谋长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:34.56,0:42:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我67年就到了这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:38.20,0:42:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫程玉芳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:41.52,0:42:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,参加工作三年了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:44.32,0:42:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我的爱人是三营的营长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:47.68,0:42:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你们有工资吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:50.28,0:42:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:51.28,0:42:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,多少钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:53.28,0:42:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,每个人20元
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:55.84,0:42:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你们需要这些钱吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:00.32,0:43:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不需要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:01.08,0:43:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱人每个月90元钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:03.64,0:43:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,一家人足够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:05.32,0:43:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不是为了钱工作的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:07.08,0:43:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,而是转变自己的观念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:10.60,0:43:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你家需要你在这里的工资
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:19.32,0:43:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我工作是为人民服务
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:21.32,0:43:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不是养家的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:24.96,0:43:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:27.12,0:43:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱人的工资足够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:29.20,0:43:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:31.88,0:43:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得自己不能整天坐着无所事事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:35.92,0:43:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也有双手 要利用起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:42.32,0:43:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,男女在政治上是平等的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:46.32,0:43:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,经济上也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:49.76,0:43:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,男同志能做到的事情 我们也可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:54.36,0:43:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,女同志可以顶起半边天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:28.64,0:44:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,战士们和农民一起建大坝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:32.12,0:44:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,在营地8公里之外的村里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:42.96,0:44:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,这些战士在帮村民建文化中心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:58.60,0:46:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,每个连队和一个村子相关联
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:01.32,0:46:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,战士们每个星期过来帮一次忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:04.28,0:46:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,事情多或者收割的时候他们会留久一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:59.12,0:47:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,仔细看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:00.72,0:47:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,然后你试一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:03.72,0:47:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,右脚退到这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:08.84,0:47:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,左脚向前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:11.68,0:47:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,摆好位置之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:14.48,0:47:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,把弹头放低一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:18.76,0:47:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,进了炮弹之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:19.72,0:47:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,往里面看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:22.44,0:47:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,用右手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:24.32,0:47:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,把炮弹推进去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:27.20,0:47:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,大概一尺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:31.04,0:47:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,这样推
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:33.88,0:47:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,用力推
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:37.28,0:47:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:38.16,0:47:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我们试试
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:00.32,0:48:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,这样不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:02.20,0:48:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,用最大的力推
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:03.32,0:48:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,只要推一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:05.32,0:48:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,用力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:13.32,0:48:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,炮弹应该放在这个手上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:16.16,0:48:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,部队最重要的工作之一是训练民兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:20.80,0:48:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,无论是城市还是农村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:22.92,0:48:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,几百万男女同志都参加军训
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:27.56,0:48:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,部队本身很小
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:29.76,0:48:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,会组织一些大型合作活动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:32.84,0:48:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,民兵负责当地的保卫工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:37.16,0:48:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,民兵也是武装力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:39.32,0:48:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,受过大型武器的训练
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:11.60,0:49:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,鱼塘底下的泥被用作肥料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:44.32,0:51:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,1937年毛泽东说过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:46.76,0:51:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,军队必须和人民保持紧密联系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:49.48,0:51:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,所以人们才把军队当成自己的军队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:52.36,0:51:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,这样的军队才是不可战胜的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:54.92,0:51:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,和人民保持紧密联系仍然是军队的目标之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:59.24,0:52:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这和传统军队是不同的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:01.16,0:52:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,传统军队是孤立的、自傲的、冷漠的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:05.32,0:52:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,中国的战士们帮助群众
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:07.24,0:52:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,也向群众学习
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:09.68,0:52:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,社会主义革命期间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:11.84,0:52:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,红军主要是农民组成的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:14.08,0:52:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,战士们和农民还是一起劳动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:18.44,0:52:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,他们的命运和革命紧密相连

